Det Insp Mark Bellamy said: "At this time we are not sure what has happened and are trying to determine the man's movements over the last few days."
The cafe is on the main road between Shrewsbury and Welshpool.
Witnesses, or anyone who saw anything suspicious in the area, are asked to call West Mercia Police.
